// Build-time AI action: reads your industry's liability landscape, past incident patterns,
// and regulatory environment → generates PATTERN declarations for LegalHygieneAdvisor.
// Run once when deploying to a new industry vertical; re-run when regulatory environment changes.
ACTION GenerateLegalHygienePatterns {
  INPUT  industry: string, regulatory_frameworks: string, past_incident_summary: string
  OUTPUT hygiene_patterns: string
  AI     "Generate Agicore PATTERN declarations for the LegalHygieneAdvisor MODULE based on the provided industry, regulatory frameworks, and incident history. Focus on: (1) industry-specific phrases that signal documented non-compliance, (2) litigation anticipation language common in this vertical, (3) privilege waiver scenarios specific to this regulatory environment, (4) any industry-specific cover-up or suppression patterns. Output valid Agicore PATTERN DSL only."
}

